Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:29.48,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}想试着谈场猜谜般的恋爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:32.03,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.94,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}虽然害怕…但还是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:40.41,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安稳度日 也太无趣了点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:45.16,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改变些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:48.88,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要个契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.54,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飞奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:54.71,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回忆在骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:02:00.30,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像认识你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:04.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不论是晴天雨天还是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.19,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.60,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从过去到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:09.85,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从明天到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.73,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 时间 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:18.53,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前烦恼的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:24.41,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}来展开新的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:29.50,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}又在做梦吗？现在的梦还不能说！
